:

*Navodno* je on bio na putu. (Apparently he was travelling.)
Ona je *navodno* želela da učini to. (She allegedly wanted to do it.)
*Navodno* postoji čudno stvorenje u šumi. (Apparently there is a strange creature in the forest.)
Oni su *navodno* bili svedoci događaja. (They were allegedly witnesses of the event.)
*Navodno* je to najbolja stvar što možeš da uradiš. (Apparently that's the best thing you can do.)